{"tid":1310472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不會出賣警隊的潛台詞就是會出賣警隊。","createTime":"2019-07-12T16:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:15:10.000Z","uid":105538,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98ce30e52f9e2058b048047029140f6bae7c2d15","tid":1310472,"uid":105538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"表達支持可以有好多詞彙<br />\n<br />\n但永遠只係用雙重否定句<br />\n<br />\n一日到黑講唔會出賣邊個果個<br />\n<br />\n從語意心理分析睇<br />\n<br />\n其實心裡一直有依個盤算<br />\n<br />\n佢既思路就係 只有要出賣 還是 未打算出賣<br />\n<br />\n所以不會出賣警隊 的意思其實就係 未打算出賣警隊 <br />\n<br />\n直至佢個利用價值低個負面影響成本<br />\n<br />\n就會正式割席"},{"pid":"ac0eec0705b99e62417c774dedc4ab143d5fe520","tid":1310472,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"講到咁罷明知黑警係賤但我包庇吹咩咁啵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}